Decisions
---------
- Step 08 branched from origin/main (64523da, PR #8) so the PR diff shows only
  Step 08.
- Force-sync uses a coalescing buffered(1) trigger; the UI guards forceSync on
  !m.syncing so the inflight counter is never double-counted, and the manual sweep
  re-lights the spinner (the automatic periodic case still lacks a sweep-start
  signal, left as the Step 07 note).
- Resize re-render reads the store cache with a nil provider (never the network);
  list items are body-less, so the body is genuinely not resident and must be
  re-fetched to re-wrap -- reviewers verified this is correct, not wasteful.
- Theming: lipgloss v2 has no AdaptiveColor; used lipgloss.LightDark over the
  detected background instead.
- Transient errors clear on the next keypress (the design's "or on next key"
  option), chosen over a tick timer for determinism.
- CI intentionally skipped per the [2] decision.
